OL,3,CTeen found guilty of manslaughter over
OL,4,Cdeath of man, 18, in Bournemouth
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's Richard Slee
OL,7,Freported on the trial from Bournemouth
OL,8,FCrown Court.
OL,10,FA teenager from Southsea has been
OL,11,Ffound guilty of the manslaughter of an
OL,12,F18-year-old man in Bournemouth last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FOn Friday, a jury ruled that Thomas
OL,16,FBetteridge, 18, was not guilty of the
OL,17,Fmurder of Cameron Hamilton, who died
OL,18,Fduring a fight in Bournemouth town
OL,19,Fcentre.
