OL,6,FCameron was pronounced dead at the
OL,7,Fscene following the altercation in the
OL,8,Farea of The Square at 1.26am on
OL,9,FSaturday 5 August 2023.
OL,11,FDuring evidence, the court was shown
OL,12,FCCTV footage of police officers
OL,13,Fchasing a group of youths through the
OL,14,Ftown.
OL,16,FThe video shows the moment before
OL,17,FBetteridge, seen wearing grey
OL,18,Fclothing, turns on the men chasing him
OL,19,Fand stabs Cameron Hamilton.
