OL,6,FWATCH: CCTV shows the moments before
OL,7,FCameron Hamilton was killed in
OL,8,FBournemouth town centre.
OL,10,FA short time afterwards, Betteridge
OL,11,Fand his friend Lennie Hansen, 18, also
OL,12,Ffrom Southsea, were detained by
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,FBetteridge was arrested and was put in
OL,16,Fthe back of a police van, where he was
OL,17,Fthen re-arrested for murder.
