OL,6,FDuring the trial, the defence accepted
OL,7,Fthat Betteridge had inflicted the
OL,8,Ffatal blow to Cameron - but claimed it
OL,9,Fwas in self defence.
OL,11,FThe prosecution had argued that
OL,12,Falthough Cameron had started the
OL,13,Ffight, Betteridge had used excessive
OL,14,Fforce by stabbing him three times.
OL,16,FA jury ruled that Hansen, was found
OL,17,Fnot guilty of assisting an offender,
OL,18,Falthough he had earlier pleaded guilty
OL,19,Fto possession of a knife.
