OL,6,FThe two men are due to be sentenced in
OL,7,FApril.
OL,9,FLast summer, Cameron Hamilton's family
OL,10,Fissued the following tribute: "Cam is
OL,11,Floved so much by his whole family, we
OL,12,Fask that our privacy is respected at
OL,13,Fthis devastating time. We have not
OL,14,Flost our beautiful boy, he has been
OL,15,Ftaken.
OL,17,F"We don't want this to be what Cam is
OL,18,Fremembered for, we want him to be
OL,19,Fremembered for the funny, kind and
OL,20,Fwonderful person he is and always will
OL,21,Fbe.
